#. §3: `Tactics`
#: Game.Levels.GroupWorld.L01_ZeroEqualsZero
msgid "Welcome to level one! Our goal is to prove that, inside some group §0, §1. Seems pretty simple, right? Yeah, there's no trick here. Since groups are based off sets, each element in the group will be unique and thus an equality operator is defined. The property that every element equals itself is called **reflexivity**. In Lean, we can cite the property using the §2 tactic. You can learn more about it, and future other tactics, by clicking on the §3 section on the right and selecting it."
msgstr ""

#: Game.Levels.GroupWorld.L04_LeftCancellation
